n. 汇款 【英】 n. 汇款(transmittal of moneyas to a distant place) 【例】 send sb. regular remittances(定期汇 款给某人) n. 汇款(寄钱给在远方的人) 【记】re反复, mit送, tance－反复送出的money－汇款 【记】remit 送 + ance ounce 盎司，送出若干盎司钱 remittance (n.)  1705; see remit + -ance. Earlier in same sense were remitment (1610s of offenses; 1670s of money sent); remital (1590s).
